## Adding Documentation

1. Add your markdown files, text files, or documentation to the `knowledge-base/` directory
2. Organize files in subdirectories as needed
3. The navigator will search all files in this directory when answering questions

Example structure:
```
knowledge-base/
├── getting-started/
│   └── quickstart.md
├── deployment/
│   ├── aws.md
│   └── kubernetes.md
